text: Tahyna MacManus (born April 24, 1986) is an Australian actress. She is known for her roles as Perri Law in the television series Blue Water High and as Emma Silverfox/Emma Frost in the superhero movie X-Men Origins: Wolverine (2009). In 2014, Tahyna married dancer Tristan MacManus.
